description	"Nik Sant

^2Weaponry:
- EC-17 Holdout Pistol (2)
- DC-15x Sniper Rifle (1)

^6Inventory:
- Seeker Drone

^8Attributes:
- Stamina (3)

^3Abilities:
- Disguise [Mind Trick] (3)
- Sprint ^3[CS1]

Nik Sant, or ''Gramps'' as he was affectionately known, was a member of the Rebel Alliance strike team sent to the forest moon of Endor.

When an Ewok stole a bike speeder, three scout troopers followed, leaving one at the shield generator. The Rebels captured the scout and Nik Sant put on the scout trooper armor."